{{ Infobox V8 Supercar race report | flag = Western Australia | title = 2014 Perth 400 | round_no = 5 | season_no = 14 | year = 2014 | series = IVSC | track_map = Barbagallo Raceway AKA Wanneroo Park (Australia) track map.svg | date = 16–18 May | location = [[Perth, Western Australia|Perth]], [[Western Australia]] | circuit = Barbagallo Raceway | weather = Fine | race1_laps = 42 | race1_dist = 100 | pole1 = [[Scott McLaughlin (racing driver)|Scott McLaughlin]] | pole1_team = [[Garry Rogers Motorsport]] | pole1_time = 55.4635 | winner1 = [[Scott McLaughlin (racing driver)|Scott McLaughlin]] | winner1_team = [[Garry Rogers Motorsport]] | winner1_time = 41:12.4849 | race2_laps = 42 | race2_dist = 100 | pole2 = [[Craig Lowndes]] | pole2_team = [[Triple Eight Race Engineering (Australia)|Triple Eight Race Engineering]] | pole2_time = 55.2979 | winner2 = [[Craig Lowndes]] | winner2_team = [[Triple Eight Race Engineering (Australia)|Triple Eight Race Engineering]] | winner2_time = 40:59.4868 | race3_laps = 83 | race3_dist = 200 | pole3 = [[Craig Lowndes]] | pole3_team = [[Triple Eight Race Engineering (Australia)|Triple Eight Race Engineering]] | pole3_time = 55.2266 | winner3 = [[Chaz Mostert]] | winner3_team = [[Ford Performance Racing]] | winner3_time = 1:21:35.0015 }}
The '''2014 Perth 400''' was a motor race meeting for the Australian sedan-based [[V8 Supercars]]. It was the fifth event of the [[2014 International V8 Supercars Championship]]. It was held on the weekend of 16-18 May at the [[Barbagallo Raceway]], near [[Wanneroo, Western Australia|Wanneroo]], [[Western Australia, Australia|Western Australia]].
