 Hausen Brewmasters]] |- | {{pbay|1985}} !scope="row" style="background-color:#FFFF99"| {{sortname|Ricardo|Brown|Ricardo Brown (basketball)}}* | [[Guard (basketball)|Guard]] | {{USA}} | [[Great Taste Coffee Makers]] |- | {{pbay|1986}} !scope="row" style="background-color:#FFFF99"| {{sortname|Ramon|Fernandez}}* (3) | [[Center (basketball)|Center]] | {{PHI}} | [[Tanduay Rhum Makers]] |- | {{pbay|1987}} !scope="row" style="background-color:#FFFF99"| {{sortname|Abet|Guidaben}}* (2) | [[Center (basketball)|Center]] | {{PHI}} | [[San Miguel Beermen]] |- | {{pbay|1988}} !scope="row" style="background-color:#FFFF99"| {{sortname|Ramon|Fernandez}}* (4) | [[Center (basketball)|Center]] | {{PHI}} | [[San Miguel Beermen]] (2) |- | {{pbay|1989}} !scope="row" style="background-color:#FFFF99"| {{sortname|Benjie|Paras}}* | [[Center (basketball)|Center]] | {{PHI}} | [[Formula Shell Zoom Masters]] |- | {{pbay|1990}} !scope="row" style="background-color:#FFFF99"| {{sortname|Allan|Caidic}}* | [[Guard (basketball)|Guard]] | {{PHI}} | [[Presto Tivolis]] |- | {{pbay|1991}} !scope="row" style="background-color:#FFFF99"| {{sortname|Alvin|Patrimonio}}* | [[Forward (basketball)|Forward]] | {{PHI}} | [[Purefoods TJ Hotdogs]] |- | {{pbay|1992}} | {{sortname|Ato|Agustin}} | [[Guard (basketball)|Guard]] | {{PHI}} | [[San Miguel Beermen]] (3) |- | {{pbay|1993}} !scope="row" style="background-color:#FFFF99"| {{sortname|Alvin|Patrimonio}}* (2) | [[Forward (basketball)|Forward]] | {{PHI}} | [[Purefoods TJ Hotdogs]] (2) |- | {{pbay|1994}} !scope="row" style="background-color:#FFFF99"| {{sortname|Alvin|Patrimonio}}* (3) | [[Forward (basketball)|Forward]] | {{PHI}} | [[Purefoods TJ Hotdogs]] (3) |- | {{pbay|1995}} | {{sortname|Vergel|Meneses}} | [[Forward (basketball)|Forward]] | {{PHI}} | [[Sunkist Orange Juicers]] |- | {{pbay|1996}} | {{sortname|Johnny|Abarrientos}} | [[Guard (basketball)|Guard]] | {{PHI}} | [[Alaska Milkmen]] |- | {{pbay|1997}} !scope="row" style="background-color:#FFFF99"| {{sortname