{{unreferenced|date=June 2012}} {{Infobox organization | name = Zamboanga Football Association | image = ZamboangaFA.png | image_border = | size = 150 | caption = | abbreviation = | motto = | formation = | founder = | type = Football association | headquarters = [[Zamboanga City]] | location = | region = | coords = | membership = | leader_title = [[President]] | leader_name = Carlo M. Rodriguez | sec_gen = | parent_organization = [[Philippine Football Federation]] | website = }}
The '''Zamboanga Football Association''' is a [[Philippines|Filipino]] [[Association football|football]] association based in [[Zamboanga City]]. It works under the [[Philippine Football Federation]] as provincial football association for the Zamboanga province. The Zamboanga FA sends a team to represent the region in the yearly [[PFF National Men's Club Championship]].
